{"tid":1060948,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"【攻美劇界】陳法拉拍住妮歌潔曼演HBO新劇","createTime":"2019-03-14T05:23:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-15T04:07:43.000Z","uid":41343,"like":37,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"031e826a9df24927993ecf194c329cbfb33bf85d","tid":1060948,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-14T05:23:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190314/large/1552533983_fe81.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190314%2Flarge%2F1552533983_fe81.jpg&h=f7f83dd8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nHBO近年推出多套自家製大熱劇，包括《權力遊戲》 （Game of Thrones）、《西部世界》（Westworld）及《小謊言》（Big Little Lies）等，近日亦拍板開拍改編自Jean Hanff Korelitz小說《You Should Have Known》的全新迷你劇《The Undoing》，主角有英國男星曉格蘭特（Hugh Grant）、金像影后妮歌潔曼（Nicole Kidman）、加拿大老戲骨當奴修打蘭（Donald Sutherland），連來自香港的陳法拉亦在演員名單之上。<br />\n<br />\n《The Undoing》是一套六集的連續劇，曉格蘭特在劇中與妮歌潔曼扮演夫妻，故事講述妮歌是個生活美滿的治療師Grace Sachs，不僅有個好丈夫，入讀名校的乖仔亦令她感到安慰，可是在其首本著作推出前夕，丈夫突然失蹤，接連的衝擊令她徬徨無助。至於首拍美劇的陳法拉，於IMDb網站中資料所見，她今次飾演Jolene一角，在六集中佔有四集戲份，亦是一個重要角色。"},{"pid":"926405f2a81e340980e63fc1e8c7faed3a484de9","tid":1060948,"uid":48369,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-14T05:39:13.000Z","msg":"fala<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"977b6d20c734f5420048e10678eb48e95c6a0c3e","tid":1060948,"uid":33408,"like":51,"dislike":0,"score":51,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-14T05:47:48.000Z","msg":"離開TVB既下場"},{"pid":"fff055138e8522726b0c72adec300a6e1ad65902","tid":1060948,"uid":146781,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-14T07:14:51.000Z","msg":"法拉nude<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" 